{"capsule_id": "claude_code_2025_07_14_a0d1aad6442143e8", "type": "reasoning_trace", "content": "Claude Code interaction: How do I create a REST API with FastAPI?...", "input_data": "How do I create a REST API with FastAPI?", "output": "Here's how to create a REST API with FastAPI:\n\n```python\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\n\napp = FastAPI()\n\nclass Item(BaseModel):\n    name: str\n    price: float\n\n@app.get(\"/\")\ndef read_root():\n    return {\"Hello\": \"World\"}\n\n@app.post(\"/items/\")\ndef create_item(item: Item):\n    return item\n```\n\nTo run this:\n1. Install FastAPI: `pip install fastapi uvicorn`\n2. Save the code as `main.py`\n3. Run: `uvicorn main:app --reload`\n\nThis creates a basic API with GET and POST endpoints.", "reasoning": "[{\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code generation detected\", \"weight\": 0.1, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:42:41.972179\"}, {\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Learning/explanation content\", \"weight\": 0.15000000000000002, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:42:41.972182\"}, {\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Technical depth in response\", \"weight\": 0.2, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:42:41.972184\"}]", "model_version": "claude-sonnet-4-conversation-monitor", "timestamp": "2025-07-14T22:42:41.972093Z", "agent_id": "claude-code-auto-capsule-system", "status": "SEALED", "metadata": {"interaction_type": "claude_code_conversation", "session_id": "213fad53", "turn_id": "turn_002", "significance_score": 0.7, "decision_factors": ["Code generation detected", "Learning/explanation content", "Technical depth in response"], "confidence": 0.8, "auto_selected": true, "user_id": "kay", "conversation_length": 545, "reasoning_quality": "automated_significance_analysis"}}
{"capsule_id": "claude_code_2025_07_14_6cd1839f77bc4806", "type": "reasoning_trace", "content": "Claude Code interaction: I need to set up Docker for my development environment...", "input_data": "I need to set up Docker for my development environment", "output": "Here's how to set up Docker for development:\n\n1. **Install Docker Desktop**\n   - Download from docker.com\n   - Follow installation instructions for your OS\n\n2. **Create a Dockerfile**\n```dockerfile\nFROM python:3.9\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY requirements.txt .\nRUN pip install -r requirements.txt\nCOPY . .\nCMD [\"python\", \"app.py\"]\n```\n\n3. **Create docker-compose.yml**\n```yaml\nversion: '3.8'\nservices:\n  app:\n    build: .\n    ports:\n      - \"8000:8000\"\n    volumes:\n      - .:/app\n```\n\n4. **Run your application**\n```bash\ndocker-compose up --build\n```\n\nThis setup provides isolated development environment with hot reloading.", "reasoning": "[{\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code generation detected\", \"weight\": 0.1, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:42:41.972694\"}, {\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"System setup/configuration\", \"weight\": 0.15000000000000002, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:42:41.972697\"}, {\"step_type\": \"significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Technical depth in response\", \"weight\": 0.2, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-14T22:42:41.972699\"}]", "model_version": "claude-sonnet-4-conversation-monitor", "timestamp": "2025-07-14T22:42:41.972617Z", "agent_id": "claude-code-auto-capsule-system", "status": "SEALED", "metadata": {"interaction_type": "claude_code_conversation", "session_id": "213fad53", "turn_id": "turn_004", "significance_score": 0.75, "decision_factors": ["Code generation detected", "System setup/configuration", "Technical depth in response"], "confidence": 0.8, "auto_selected": true, "user_id": "kay", "conversation_length": 669, "reasoning_quality": "automated_significance_analysis"}}
{"capsule_id": "windsurf_2025_07_15_4f7951471c6d40c5", "type": "reasoning_trace", "content": "Windsurf IDE interaction: How do I refactor this component to use React hooks?...", "input_data": "How do I refactor this component to use React hooks?", "output": "Here's how to refactor your component to use React hooks:\n\n```jsx\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react';\n\nconst MyComponent = () => {\n  const [state, setState] = useState(initialState);\n  \n  useEffect(() => {\n    // Side effects here\n  }, []);\n  \n  return (\n    <div>{/* Your JSX */}</div>\n  );\n};\n```\n\nKey changes:\n1. Replace class with function component\n2. Use useState for state management\n3. Use useEffect for lifecycle methods", "reasoning": "[{\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code generation detected\", \"weight\": 0.1, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.942495\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Learning/explanation content\", \"weight\": 0.15000000000000002, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.942500\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code completion interaction\", \"weight\": 0.2, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.942503\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code refactoring discussion\", \"weight\": 0.25, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.942506\"}]", "model_version": "windsurf-conversation-monitor", "timestamp": "2025-07-15T10:33:40.942542Z", "agent_id": "windsurf-auto-capsule-system", "status": "SEALED", "metadata": {"interaction_type": "windsurf_ide_conversation", "session_id": "0b4c5159", "turn_id": "windsurf_turn_001", "significance_score": 1.0, "decision_factors": ["Code generation detected", "Learning/explanation content", "Code completion interaction", "Code refactoring discussion"], "confidence": 0.7999999999999999, "auto_selected": true, "user_id": "kay", "conversation_length": 497, "reasoning_quality": "windsurf_s