{"capsule_id": "windsurf_2025_07_15_e30ac3806d8e4e5e", "type": "reasoning_trace", "content": "Windsurf IDE interaction: Can you explain Windsurf's Cascade feature?...", "input_data": "Can you explain Windsurf's Cascade feature?", "output": "Windsurf's Cascade feature allows you to chain multiple AI operations together for complex workflows:\n\n**Key Features:**\n- **Sequential Processing**: Each step builds on the previous\n- **Context Preservation**: Maintains context across steps\n- **Error Handling**: Graceful failure recovery\n- **Branching Logic**: Conditional execution paths\n\n**Usage Example:**\n1. Analyze code structure\n2. Identify optimization opportunities\n3. Generate refactored code\n4. Run tests to verify changes\n\nThis creates a powerful workflow that can handle complex development tasks autonomously.", "reasoning": "[{\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Code generation detected\", \"weight\": 0.1, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961770\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Learning/explanation content\", \"weight\": 0.15000000000000002, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961776\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Technical depth in response\", \"weight\": 0.2, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961780\"}, {\"step_type\": \"windsurf_significance_detection\", \"content\": \"Windsurf-specific feature discussion\", \"weight\": 0.25, \"timestamp\": \"2025-07-15T10:33:40.961783\"}]", "model_version": "windsurf-conversation-monitor", "timestamp": "2025-07-15T10:33:40.961823Z", "agent_id": "windsurf-auto-capsule-system", "status": "SEALED", "metadata": {"interaction_type": "windsurf_ide_conversation", "session_id": "0b4c5159", "turn_id": "windsurf_turn_003", "significance_score": 0.8999999999999999, "decision_factors": ["Code generation detected", "Learning/explanation content", "Technical depth in response", "Windsurf-specific feature discussion"]